{"tid":2187433,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇夜更保安哩份工","createTime":"2020-09-03T15:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T11:44:17.000Z","uid":186399,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c5c366b50d75c380d02ba10becc712b57ec1ca5c","tid":2187433,"uid":186399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:16:27.000Z","msg":"話說最近有個fd因為武肺失業，咁咪問吓佢有咩打算囉。然後佢話有朋友叫佢去返某大學嘅夜更保安，然後話人工有16K倒。咁佢又沒讀大學16K係哩個時勢的確叫多嘅，但係我始終唔太敢做夜更保安。<br />\n<br />\n想像吓，好彩既話你返工唔係自己一個坐過夜，但係通常返哩啲工嘅都係啲廢佬嚟。<br />\n你：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老屎忽：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老屎忽成晚開大個喇叭係到睇星爺套回魂夜<br />\n個配樂勁大聲係到 登登登登..........<br />\n你:<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到咗12點<br />\n老屎忽：喂！仔，你而加自己去巡一轉先，我睇哩套戲再去，咁樣大家都巡一次就夠。<br />\n你：吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老屎忽：快啦，死仔叫你做少少野都咁多廢話，沒嚟醒目嘅。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後你就死死地氣咁一個去巡<br />\n<br />\n而大學哩啲咁多後生嘅地方，就一定會有鬼故。而頭先你又因為沒嘢做走咗去查吓間大學有啲咩鬼故，而咁啱個老屎忽又叫你記得去其中一個地點到簽番本巡更簿，沒得扮巡咗嘅你唯有硬著頭皮咁去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜晚嘅校園閂哂燈，加上大學哩啲又大又開放嘅建築物，你會成日聽到有怪聲係四處傳嚟，但係你又因為唔想比個老屎忽屌所以只有繼續巡。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於到收工啦，返完成晚心血都少幾年，但係第二晚又要返工。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：生人唔生膽"},{"pid":"3f08b975cdca0fabfaed96284403d4fe54308f90","tid":2187433,"uid":44209,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:17:48.000Z","msg":"挨夜對身體唔好"},{"pid":"143f32d5e3a0b0c2f2d33e84d0399a43262e19f5","tid":2187433,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:18:00.000Z","msg":"讀唔成書要做保安<br />\n<br />\n抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167c841e9a845d5e2870fab12cf65681b2e1d849","tid":2187433,"uid":127571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:18:24.000Z","msg":"以為講故台故事"},{"pid":"e10485269cca37ec68e1532379e5952b12726b0c","tid":2187433,"uid":186399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f08b975cdca0fabfaed96284403d4fe54308f90","tid":2187433,"uid":44209,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:17:48.000Z","msg":"挨夜對身體唔好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:19:08.000Z","msg":"是<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9635d9b5b8a812e91b42421ee8638c32124d2ad5","tid":2187433,"uid":186399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"143f32d5e3a0b0c2f2d33e84d0399a43262e19f5","tid":2187433,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:18:00.000Z","msg":"讀唔成書要做保安<br />\n<br />\n抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:19:29.000Z","msg":"屈巴是對的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b05eb44b52dd70219b01492c6bfb6791aad32e","tid":2187433,"uid":186399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"167c841e9a845d5e2870fab12cf65681b2e1d849","tid":2187433,"uid":127571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:18:24.000Z","msg":"以為講故台故事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:19:45.000Z","msg":"講故師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff88c831a246c64933fc6909d62f8c1e5695179","tid":2187433,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9635d9b5b8a812e91b42421ee8638c32124d2ad5","tid":2187433,"uid":186399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"143f32d5e3a0b0c2f2d33e84d0399a43262e19f5","tid":2187433,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:18:00.000Z","msg":"讀唔成書要做保安<br />\n<br />\n抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:19:29.000Z","msg":"屈巴是對的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif